      <title>韩国股市下跌，韩元在尹永康短暂戒严后回升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/korean-won-gains-stocks-dip-after-president-s-brief-martial-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈在政治争斗中短暂宣布戒严，但数小时后又撤销戒严令，随后，韩国货币在周三早盘回升，但韩国股市下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/korean-won-gains-stocks-dip-after-president-s-brief-martial-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 00:04:42 GMT</pubDate>
